command | commit             | commands/commit.md         | Semantic commit assistant
command | prep-permissions   | commands/prep-permissions.md | Configure permissions for task execution
command | init               | commands/init.md           | Initialize .prove.json for this project
command | install-skills     | commands/install-skills.md | Install recommended community skills
command | create-command     | commands/create-command.md | Create a new Claude Code slash command
command | create-agent       | commands/create-agent.md   | Create a new Claude Code subagent
command | agentic-docs       | commands/agentic-docs.md   | Generate LLM-optimized documentation
command | progress           | commands/progress.md       | Show orchestrator execution status
